  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Whether Correction of Anemia Using Recombinant Human Erythropoietin Reduces the Progression of Atherosclerosis and Cardiac Hypertrophy in Pre-dialysis Chronic Kidney Disease Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomised Controlled Trial to Study the Effects of Recombinant Human Erythropoietin on the Progression of Atherosclerosis, Cardiovascular Function, Nutrition and Residual Renal Function in Pre-dialysis Chronic Renal Failure Patients</official_title>
