  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim of the study is to evaluate the effects of correction of anemia using
      erythropoietin on the progression of atherosclerosis and cardiac muscle thickening in
      patients with chronic kidney disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
